    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1905-01-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1905-01-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="151"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d151">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Minister <persName type="to">Conger</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-01-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 6, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 868.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I inclose herewith for your information a copy of
                    a note from the Chinese minister here,<note n="a" xml:id="d151fna">Printed
                        ante.</note> informing the Department that it is the decision of the
                    Imperial Chinese Government to cancel and annul the agreements made with the
                    American China Development Company, bearing date April 14, 1898, and July 13,
                    1900; and stating the reasons; which have forced the Chinese Government to take
                    that step.</p>
                <p>I also inclose a copy of the Department’s note to the minister, in reply.<note
                        n="a" xml:id="d151fnb">Printed ante.</note>
                </p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">F. B. Loomis.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
